    input: data/platelet_full-cohort_counts.txt, results/tables/read_coverage.txt
    output: results/readQC/totalReads_arranged.png, results/readQC/geneAttributes_barplot.png, results/readQC/biotype_barplot.png
    jobid: 1695

Rscript scripts/RNAseq_readQC.R         --countsFile=data/platelet_full-cohort_counts.txt         --readDistFile=results/tables/read_coverage.txt         --annoFile=/home/groups/CEDAR/anno/biomaRt/hg38.Ens_94.biomaRt.geneAnno.Rdata         --metaFile=./data/metadata.tsv         --plotCols="Lane,Group,Sex,Age_at_collection,Novogene_RIN"         --contrast=Group         --corType=both         --outdir=results/readQC
